ClearBlade, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:08 AM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of ClearBlade, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
ClearBlade, Inc. develops and provides a platform to build industrial Internet of Things solutions. It offers ClearBlade Novi, which enables companies to build IoT solutions that make streaming data actionable by combining business rules and machine learning with visualizations and integrations to existing business systems. The platform runs securely in any vendor cloud, on-premise, or in hybrid environments. ClearBlade, Inc. was founded in 2007 and is based in Austin, Texas with an additional office in Raleigh, North Carolina.


103 East 5th StreetSuite 203Austin, TX 78701United StatesFounded in 2007



Phone: 512-686-3037

