IoT Agenda
















blog




Aaron Allsbrook, ClearBlade CTO and product visionary for the Novi IoT platform, brings decades of application development tooling and runtime experience to emerging technologies in the Industrial Internet of Things.
Early on, Aaron engineered software at IBM building scalable performant platforms for developers to design, develop and execute modern workloads. As a practitioner, Aaron worked directly in the field with enterprises to enable cutting-edge solutions while leveraging existing technical assets. Today, he provides a depth of expertise necessary to understand the challenges, opportunities and transitions required for enterprises engaging with the Industrial Internet of Things.







