ClearBlade, Inc.


                  ClearBlade, Inc. operates service platform to describe and manage mobile applications. The firm specializes in IoT Runtime, enterprise, Internet of things and development, MQTT messaging, mainframe, Serverless, IIoT, Containerized, Integrations and ESB. The company was founded by Eric Simone in 2007 and is headquartered in Austin, TX.                




